            "id": 5900351,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大跌1%，報40938.79點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間13日11:38，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>下跌412.14點（或1%），暫報40938.79點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-3.85%</li><li>近 1 月：-6.8%</li><li>近 3 月：-5.84%</li><li>近 6 月：+0.62%</li><li>今年以來：-2.8%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)領跌。賽富時(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRM-US</a>)下跌4.25%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)下跌3.41%；亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)下跌1.88%；3M(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MMM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MMM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MMM-US</a>)下跌1.71%；華特迪士尼(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DIS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DIS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DIS-US</a>)下跌1.64%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，威瑞森電信(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VZ:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VZ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VZ-US</a>)上漲2.54%；默克藥廠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)上漲1.74%；旅行家集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TRV:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TRV\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TRV-US</a>)上漲1.36%；麥當勞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MCD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MCD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MCD-US</a>)上漲0.86%；雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)上漲0.72%。</p></section></main>",
